A Django Dummy Data Provider


Dependencies
============

- Python (Scripting Language)
- Django (Web Framework)
- South (Django Schema Migration)
- Tastypie (Django REST Framework)
- Haystack (Django Search Module)
- Mutagen (Python audio/video tag library)
## REMOVED - Grappelli (advanced django-admin interface)
## REMOVED - Filebrowser (django-admin file browser)
- Haystack (search provider)
- Whoosh (search engine) - not integrated yet
- LXML (for xml rest responses)


Installation
============

* Requires a python installation

$ easy_install pip
$ sudo pip install django south django-tastypie mutagen django-haystack whoosh

$ sudo pip install lxml

Note: For Mac you need to "export ARCHFLAGS=-arch i386 -arch x86_64" for LXML to build correct

Setup
=====

$ ./manage.py syncdb
$ ./manage.py migrate --all
$ ./manage.py scanmusic <music-folder> (~/media/music)
$ ./manage.py scanmovies <movies-folder> (~/media/movies)
$ ./manage.py scanphotos <photos-folder> (~/media/photos)
$ ./manage.py scancontacts data/names.csv
$ ./manage.py runserver

open browser at http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin

REST API
========

* base: http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/
* contacts: http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/contacts/?format=json
* music: http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/music/?format=json
* movies: http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/movies/?format=json
* radio: http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/radio/?format=json


Query Examples
==============

base api:
- http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1?format=json

contacts base api:
- http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/contacts/?format=json

schema
- http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/contacts/schema/?format=json

extended limit
- http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/contacts/?format=json&limit=100

skip pagination:
- http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/contacts/?format=json&limit=0

list entries
- http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/contacts/?format=json

set of objects
- http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/contacts/set/1;3/?format=json

filtering
- http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/contacts/?format=json&zip_code__gte=07974
- http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/contacts/?format=json&zip_code=07974

details
- http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/contacts/6/?format=json

ordering
- http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/contacts/?format=json&zip_code__gte=07974&order_by=city

full text search
- http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/contacts/search/?format=json&q=Robinson


